videos.description: V.J. Beachem shows great focus and hits a runner early in the first half for Notre Dame against Purdue.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Notre Dame's Beachem hits the runner) 2016/12/17

videos.headline: Notre Dame's Beachem hits the runner

videos.description: Carsen Edwards steals the ball on back-to-back plays for Purdue, resulting in a big dunk for Caleb Swanigan and a layup.
videos.headline: Purdue turning defense into big offense

videos.description: Notre Dame is off and running against Purdue ending with Martinas Geben throwing down the two-hand slam.
videos.headline: Huge dunk punctuates Notre Dame's 7-0 run

videos.description: Notre Dame's Matt Farrell knocks down a big 3-pointer  as the Fighting Irish start to pull away in the first half.
videos.headline: Farrell pads Notre Dame's lead with 3-pointer

videos.description: Notre Dame's V.J. Beachem passes up the 3-pointer in order to throw down a big baseline jam.
videos.headline: Beachum passes up shot to throw down baseline jam

videos.description: Vince Edwards makes a 3-pointer to cut into Notre Dame's lead.
videos.headline: Edwards knocks down 3-pointer to cut into ND's lead

videos.description: Matt Farrell finds Austin Torres in the paint for a high-percentage shot.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's ball movement leads to easy bucket

videos.description: Ryan Cline hits a clutch 3-pointer to give Purdue its first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Purdue takes its first lead of the game

videos.description: Purdue's Caleb Swanigan scores down low and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Swanigan gets the bucket plus the foul

videos.description: Caleb Swanigan finds himself all alone under the hoop and throws down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Swanigan's dunk helps Purdue maintain lead
